<td sourcefile="../../Documentation.ja/README_MRTKStandardShader.md" sourcestartlinenumber="36">Enables an additive blending mode, which sums the previous pixel color with the current pixel color. This is the preferred transparency mode to avoid transparency sorting issues.</td>
